			<div class="post_box hentry">
				<div class="headline_area">
					<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy">Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy</a></h2>
					<p class="headline_meta">by <span class="author vcard fn">Joe Abley</span> on <abbr class="published" title="2012-10-29">October 29, 2012</abbr></p>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text entry-content">
<p>ICANN is responsible for the management of the root zone&#8217;s DNSSEC Key Signing Key (KSK). This responsibility includes secure storage of cryptographic key material in redundant Key Management Facilities (KMFs) located within the USA, one in Culpeper, Virginia and one in El Segundo, California. Despite the damage and concern caused by Hurricane Sandy as it [&hellip;]</p>
<p><span class='st_facebook_buttons' st_title='Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy' st_url='http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/' displayText='Facebook'></span><span class='st_twitter_buttons' st_title='Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy' st_url='http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/' displayText='Twitter'></span><span class='st_email_buttons' st_title='Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy' st_url='http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/' displayText='Email'></span><span class='st_sharethis_buttons' st_title='Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy' st_url='http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/' displayText='ShareThis'></span><span class='st_fblike_buttons' st_title='Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy' st_url='http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/' displayText='Facebook Like'></span><span class='st_plusone_buttons' st_title='Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy' st_url='http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/' displayText='Google +1'></span><span class='st_pinterest _buttons' st_title='Root Zone KSK vs. Hurricane Sandy' st_url='http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/' displayText='Pinterest'></span></p>					<p class="to_comments"><span class="bracket">{</span> <a href="http://blog.icann.org/2012/10/root-zone-ksk-vs-hurricane-sandy/#comments" rel="nofollow"><span>0</span> comments</a> <span class="bracket">}</span></p>
